## 3. How we work — the `feature-workflow` skill
Every change follows `.claude/skills/feature-workflow/SKILL.md`:
capture the requirement → ground in the KB/code → decide (record notable choices; ask the owner only
on big/irreversible/conflicting calls) → implement small slices → self-test ({{GATE}}) → review with
subagents → verify for real → sync the KB → commit (push when asked). Large, multi-module initiatives
mature a per-module **FRD** (`knowledgebase/frds/`) before becoming a plan; small changes skip it.

